\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Chattanooga is a premier dog-friendly destination, offering unique venues like Play Wash Pint brewery and the expansive Tennessee Riverwalk along the waterfront.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Chattanooga, TN, lives up to its \\\\\\\"Scenic City\\\\\\\" moniker with a dog-friendly infrastructure that rivals major metropolitan areas. The city boasts an impressive array of parks, including \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.chattanooga.gov/parks-recreation\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Heritage Park Dog Park\\\"}],null,\\\" in East Brainerd with separate areas, agility equipment, and shaded seating, and the downtown \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.chattanooga.gov/parks-recreation\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Chew Chew Canine Park\\\"}],null,\\\" providing urban off-leash access. For scenic leashed walks, the \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"7\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.chattanoogariverwalk.com/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Tennessee Riverwalk\\\"}],null,\\\" offers 13 miles of paved pathways along the Tennessee River. Unique to Chattanooga is \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"10\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://playwashpint.com/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Play Wash Pint\\\"}],null,\\\", a brewery featuring pet-grade turf, wash stations, and craft beers, creating a social hub for both dogs and owners.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The city's commitment to pets is evident in its \\\\\\\"Better Cities for Pets\\\\\\\" initiatives and the abundance of dog-friendly businesses, from restaurants with patios to attractions like \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://seerockcity.com/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Rock City Gardens\\\"}],null,\\\" that welcome leashed pets on trails. The community actively celebrates dogs through events like the \\\\\\\"Running of the Chihuahuas.\\\\\\\" While Chattanooga's outdoor amenities are extensive, the humid Southern climate can limit activity during peak summer months. \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Indoor Dog Park\\\"}],null,\\\" serves as a critical resource, providing a comfortable, climate-controlled environment where Chattanooga's active dog community can thrive year-round, ensuring consistent exercise and socialization opportunities.\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta primary\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"park-directory\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-list-check\\\"}],\\\"Browse directory\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta ghost\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"map-and-neighborhoods\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-geo-alt\\\"}],\\\"Open map\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/list-your-park\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta text-link\\\",\\\"